Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.75,0:00:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bocah, aku punya permintaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.02,0:00:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.37,0:00:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin bekerja.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.53,0:00:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mau bekerja?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.77,0:00:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah muak terus-terusan jadi benalu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa denganmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.12,0:00:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tahu sendiri, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.55,0:00:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soal Teal yang selalu membawa Batu Sihir\Ntiap kali berkunjung.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.11,0:00:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dewa Pelindung, silakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.50,0:00:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berapa banyak uang yang sudah dia habiskan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.40,0:00:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau berhenti jadi benalu?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.02,0:00:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kumohon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.81,0:00:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya tekadmu sudah bulat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, mari kita mulai.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.56,0:00:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Proyek Perombakan Besar-besaran Goy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namaku Goy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.82,0:02:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin mendaftar jadi petualang.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.02,0:02:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa dokumen ini sudah benar?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.57,0:02:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Anu...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia ini teman\NPendekar Pedang Sihir Kilat Hitam.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.40,0:02:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kelihatannya memang mencurigakan,\Ntapi dia bisa dipercaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.20,0:02:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Clayman! Tuan Clayman!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?\NAku sedang sibuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.64,0:02:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan bohong!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.52,0:02:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anda hanya senyum-senyum sendiri\Nmelihat bekal dari istri Anda, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei! Jangan keras-keras!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku malas menanggapi kalian,\Njadi langsung saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:02:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada urusan apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.33,0:03:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau mendaftar jadi petualang.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memangnya tidak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pendekar Pedang Sihir itu\Nyang bertanggung jawab, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.44,0:03:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, aku jamin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.20,0:03:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nih. Pendaftarannya sudah selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.86,0:03:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, besok aku akan datang\Nuntuk mengambil permintaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong siapkan permintaan untuk pemula.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.34,0:03:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai jumpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau tak ambil permintaan\Nhari ini saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.20,0:03:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Butuh persiapan senjata\Ndan semacamnya, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.91,0:03:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa pakai sihir...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.75,0:03:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nah, itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.95,0:03:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau pakai sihir kegelapan,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}identitasmu sebagai kaum iblis\Nakan ketahuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.17,0:03:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, berhati-hatilah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, kau belum tahu apa-apa\Nsoal Minerva, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.55,0:03:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari ini, aku akan memandumu seharian.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.77,0:03:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf merepotkanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.04,0:03:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bicara apa kau ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.64,0:03:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau akan jadi rekan\NPendekar Pedang Sihir Kilat Hitam!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.51,0:03:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau itu, aku tolak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku datang untuk ambil permintaan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.37,0:03:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pagi-pagi sudah berisik.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:04:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, ada tamu untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.35,0:04:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamu untuk Pendekar Pedang Sihir\NKilat Hitam ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.68,0:04:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ada insiden baru?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.42,0:04:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia menunggumu di belakang gedung.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan buat dia menunggu lama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.82,0:04:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah menunggumu,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.42,0:04:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Pendekar Pedang Sihir Kilat Hitam.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.01,0:04:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cecilia?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.39,0:04:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kuduga, ternyata memang kau, Youki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.52,0:04:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}I-Ini, anu, bukan begitu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namaku bukan Youki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.48,0:04:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ini Pendekar Pedang Sihir Kilat Hitam!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Youki?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.86,0:04:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.17,0:04:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sadar kalau aku sedang melakukan\Nhal yang bodoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.55,0:04:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sadar juga rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kenapa bisa ketahuan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sophia yang memberitahuku
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.93,0:04:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kalau Pendekar Pedang Sihir Kilat Hitam\Nmuncul lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.04,0:04:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya aku sudah dengar rumornya\Nsejak lama,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi makin didengar,\Nsosoknya makin mirip denganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.24,0:04:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku datang untuk memastikannya
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.57,0:04:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}karena khawatir kau akan buat\Nkekacauan lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.00,0:04:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata informasinya bocor lewat Clayman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Alasanmu berpakaian begini agar Goy\Ntidak terlalu mencolok, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.84,0:05:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, kurang lebih begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.68,0:05:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurutku, kostum ini sudah paling tepat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.53,0:05:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga akan bantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Habisnya, aku khawatir kalau\NTuan Pendekar Pedang Sihir sendirian.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, mari kita mulai\Ndari permintaan untuk pemula.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akulah yang menerima permintaan\Npencarian hewan peliharaan dari Guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.66,0:05:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beri tahu aku detailnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, kliennya sampai mematung begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.28,0:05:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa dia terpesona dengan penampilanku?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.33,0:05:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Pendekar Pedang Sihir,\Nbisa tolong diam sebentar?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.28,0:05:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertama-tama,\Ntolong beri tahu ciri-ciri kucingnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.68,0:05:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Warna, ukuran, dan bentuk ekornya bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia menyimak untuk belajar, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Inilah ciri-ciri anak kucing\Nyang hilang itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ia pintar, biasanya selalu pulang sendiri,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi sejak minggu lalu, ia tidak kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.73,0:06:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana cara kita mencarinya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertama, kita tanya-tanya ke sekitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.48,0:06:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bertanya pada tetangga sekitar\Natau kesatria patroli adalah cara standar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku akan melakukan lebih dari itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.48,0:06:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hiat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan penguatan indra penciuman, aku sudah\Nmengingat aroma kucing pada si klien.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu dengan "Kilat Cepat",
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.42,0:06:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku perkuat kekuatan kaki untuk berlari\Nmengelilingi kota dan menemukannya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.02,0:06:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ketemu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa instingmu mewaspadai kekuatanku?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.13,0:06:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tenanglah, Pendekar Pedang Sihir\NKilat Hitam ini adalah kawanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa boleh buat, tidurlah sejenak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:06:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Holy Bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.46,0:07:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kucing yang satu lagi...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tadi ia bersama anak kucingmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lukanya sudah kuobati, jadi tolong rawat\Nkucing-kucing itu bersama-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, sampai jumpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.06,0:07:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa dengan begini permintaannya selesai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.22,0:07:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tinggal melapor ke Guild\Nkalau permintaannya sudah selesai,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.73,0:07:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan kita akan menerima imbalan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.66,0:07:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo ke permintaan berikutnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu sebentar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cara Tuan Pendekar Pedang Sihir itu\Ntidak bisa ditiru sembarang orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.71,0:07:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini tidak akan jadi pengalaman\Nuntuk Goy, lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kali ini, biarkan Goy yang memimpin,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.93,0:07:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan sebisa mungkin biarkan dia\Nmelakukannya sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.51,0:07:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ba-Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.08,0:07:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi tolong pandu jalannya, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.95,0:07:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak hafal wilayah sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak ada yang perlu dikhawatirkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,0:07:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di belakangmu ada aku,\NPendekar Pedang Sihir Kilat Hitam!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, ini obat herbalnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengar, Goy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengumpulkan obat herbal adalah jalan\Nyang pasti dilalui semua petualang.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan ambil lebih dari yang dibutuhkan,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.31,0:08:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}karena itu akan menyulitkan petualang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm, aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa sebegini sudah cukup?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, bagus sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.44,0:08:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan begini, Goy sudah selangkah\Nlebih dekat menuju puncak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, ayo ke permintaan selanjutnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permintaan selanjutnya\Nadalah membasmi Goblin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagi Goy, ini akan jadi\Npertempuran pertamanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.93,0:08:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita harus mendukungnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.16,0:08:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hiat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.90,0:08:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hiat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.71,0:08:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya dia tak butuh bantuan kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.84,0:08:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Inilah kekuatan cinta...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan, ini kekuatan orang\Nyang ogah jadi benalu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.08,0:08:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bukan benalu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.35,0:08:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Misi ini selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.71,0:08:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini upahmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.77,0:08:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, begini rasanya bekerja.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:08:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal fisik Teal lemah,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.84,0:09:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi dia bekerja keras mencari uang\Nseperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan terus bekerja keras,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.97,0:09:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan membalas budi pada Teal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semangat yang bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari kita berjuang bersama, Goy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.75,0:09:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan mendukungmu sekuat tenaga besok.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi mulai dari sini,\Nbisakah aku melakukannya sendiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.77,0:09:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau belum bisa sendirian...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.28,0:09:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak akan membuat masalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.11,0:09:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah paham\Ncara menyelesaikan permintaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau harus kembali dengan selamat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadilah kuat sampai kau layak menjadi\Ntangan kanan Pendekar Pedang Sihir ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.06,0:09:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan menantikannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nah, matahari sudah terbenam.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Waktunya berpisah untuk sementara.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.39,0:09:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau punya rencana setelah ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mumpung aku sedang menjadi\NPendekar Pedang Sihir Kilat Hitam,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.62,0:09:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku akan mengambil Misi Peringkat A.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.71,0:09:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga ikut.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, tapi Misi Peringkat A biasanya\Nbutuh waktu beberapa hari perjalanan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.35,0:10:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cecilia sibuk, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.35,0:10:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang tidak masalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.40,0:10:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa aku merepotkanmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja aku senang.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.37,0:10:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi walau ini misi,\Nrasanya akan seperti perjalanan jauh, lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.97,0:10:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biasanya kita cuma minum teh berduaan,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}atau pergi bareng orang lain, tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau pergi berdua selama beberapa hari?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ta-Tapi dengan pakaianmu itu,\Npasti sulit untuk berkemah di luar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.02,0:10:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau juga tak punya perlengkapan\Nperjalanan jauh, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.17,0:10:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, tolong tunggu sebentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.22,0:10:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf membuatmu menunggu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.66,0:10:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku Cecily, seorang petualang.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cecily?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah menyiapkan perlengkapan,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.31,0:10:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan dengan pakaian ini, takkan ada yang tahu\Nkalau aku ini Cecilia dari Party Pahlawan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.55,0:10:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak masalah, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Clayman tadi terlihat sangat senang, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.35,0:11:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katanya permintaan yang merepotkan\Nakhirnya beres,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi ini cuma investigasi reruntuhan, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.66,0:11:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kedengarannya mudah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permintaan Peringkat A tak selalu\Nsoal melawan monster kuat, lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Misalnya, dalam perjalanan\Nmenuju reruntuhan ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.35,0:11:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tidak ada desa untuk\Nbersinggah dan istirahat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.97,0:11:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya. Jalannya juga buruk, repot sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.82,0:11:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memastikan rute menuju reruntuhan\Nitu berbahaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, kita harus menginvestigasi\Ntanpa merusak bagian dalamnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.22,0:11:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ingat, dilarang keras\Nmenggunakan sihir serangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lantas bagaimana kalau monster muncul?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.68,0:11:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hindari pertempuran sebisa mungkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.88,0:11:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena misi ini juga mencakup\Npenelitian ekosistem monsternya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.04,0:11:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Banyak sekali aturannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kliennya adalah arkeolog\Ndari lembaga penelitian negara,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi bagi Guild, ini permintaan penting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.42,0:11:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Pendekar Pedang Sihir\Nmemang sangat dipercaya, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.28,0:11:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, aku harus berusaha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.37,0:11:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari kita siapkan tempat berkemah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berkemah berduaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.68,0:12:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Melewati malam hanya berdua.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.51,0:12:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau aku yang biasanya,\Naku pasti sudah panik dan gugup.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi sekarang tidak masalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.40,0:12:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.95,0:12:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku akan menutupi semuanya\Ndengan Mode Chuuni.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.35,0:12:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akulah Pendekar Pedang Sihir Kilat Hitam.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berkemah pun akan kubuat\Nsempurna dan nyaman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keamanan di sekitar sini sudah kupastikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.73,0:12:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}buah-buahan dan tanaman liar untuk\Nbahan makanan juga sudah kukumpulkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau terampil sekali, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena tak ada orang lain,\Nbagaimana kalau topengnya dilepas saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.74,0:12:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja tidak bisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.44,0:12:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai misi selesai, aku adalah\NPendekar Pedang Sihir Kilat Hitam.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.73,0:12:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memperlihatkan wajah adalah hal tabu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.66,0:12:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Topeng ini didesain\Nagar aku tetap bisa makan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:12:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu tidak sopan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.08,0:13:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, maaf. Aku lepas sendiri saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan kutuangkan supnya, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.91,0:13:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini cuma sup sederhana, tapi silakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enak sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.57,0:13:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mana mungkin masakan Cecilia tidak enak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.53,0:13:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau berlebihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.20,0:13:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}I-Itu kenyataannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.35,0:13:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih makanannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.37,0:13:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pakai lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.53,0:13:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wahai jiwaku, tenanglah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.46,0:13:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kau kelihatan sangat panik.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Be-Begitu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya ampun, gawat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.08,0:13:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Besok kita harus bangun pagi,\Njadi ayo tidur.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sudah mau tidur?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.44,0:13:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manisnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.13,0:14:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi sepertinya hari ini Cecilia\Nsedikit berbeda dari biasanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi Cecilia juga...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.88,0:14:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Panggil aku Cecily.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.46,0:14:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.55,0:14:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cecily pasti lelah karena sudah bekerja\Nsejak pagi, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.40,0:14:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau pikir aku ini siapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ini anggota Party Pahlawan yang terpilih\Nuntuk mengalahkan Raja Iblis
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan sudah menyelesaikan lebih banyak\Npermintaan daripada Tuan Pendekar Pedang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bercanda. Aku cuma meniru\Ngaya bicaramu tadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.68,0:14:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengagetkan saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.28,0:14:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mohon maaf, aku harus menolaknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pengalamanku masih belum cukup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.37,0:14:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku belum berniat menikah dengan siapa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.17,0:14:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi pria menarik itu ditolak, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tidak ada hubungannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.57,0:14:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi alasan itu tak bisa digunakan\Nuntuk menolak orang yang satu ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.11,0:15:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pewaris penguasa wilayah tetangga\Nyang berpengaruh
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}telah mengajukan lamaran resmi untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo pergi, Cecily!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.53,0:15:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Petualangan yang belum pernah kita lihat\Ntelah menunggu kita!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Pendekar Pedang Sihir,\Njangan bicara keras-keras.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.11,0:15:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nanti bisa memancing monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.26,0:15:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari ini aku yang akan ada di garis depan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.15,0:15:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh? Biasanya terbalik, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sihirmu terlalu kuat\Ndan bisa merusak reruntuhan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.55,0:15:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika terjadi sesuatu, aku bisa\Nmenahan monsternya dengan Saint Chain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.54,0:15:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, serahkan padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu posisi para monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, aku punya sihir\Nyang belum pernah kutunjukkan padamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.75,0:16:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada monster di depan sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jumlahnya sekitar 13 ekor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.48,0:16:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luar biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.64,0:16:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jumlahnya tepat sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi jumlahnya terlalu banyak untuk ditahan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebaiknya kita memutar arah\Nuntuk menghindari pertempuran.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.25,0:16:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, serahkan saja padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.15,0:16:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Illusion Sphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bisa melihat jalan di depan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita akan terus berjalan,\Njadi tolong tutup matamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sihir apa yang baru saja kau gunakan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.48,0:16:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sihir kegelapan tingkat menengah,\NIllusion Sphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.91,0:16:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sihir yang memunculkan ilusi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.06,0:16:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa pun yang melihatnya
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.48,0:17:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}akan melihat hal yang paling memikat\Nsehingga perhatiannya teralihkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.33,0:17:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hal yang paling memikat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.57,0:17:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Intinya hal yang disukai, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau aku,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.59,0:17:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pasti akan melihat Cecilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.91,0:17:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau Raven pasti melihat Hapyneth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.75,0:17:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kira-kira aku akan melihat apa, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja hal yang paling disukai Cecilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.91,0:17:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.27,0:17:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mungkin kue?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kok itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.42,0:17:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.13,0:17:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sihir yang sangat praktis, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.08,0:17:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Pendekar Pedang Sihir hebat\Nbisa menggunakan berbagai macam sihir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.28,0:17:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sihirku bukan cuma ini saja, lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.49,0:17:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ikuti aku dengan tenang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya reruntuhannya\Nsampai di sini saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.17,0:17:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cecily...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.48,0:17:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa reruntuhan memang sekosong ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.43,0:18:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada jamur langka di sini, lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejauh apa pun kita berjalan,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.93,0:18:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang ada cuma monster, tanaman, tanaman,\Nmonster, tanaman, jamur!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.46,0:18:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Harusnya ada sesuatu\Nyang lebih dari ini, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.65,0:18:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti Android yang tertidur ribuan tahun,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.57,0:18:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pedang sihir yang disegel, warisan kuno,\Natau harta karun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.55,0:18:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Atau setidaknya monster bos yang klise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Muncullah sesuatu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.11,0:18:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan bicara keras-keras.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.84,0:18:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari kita lihat ke luar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.77,0:18:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luar biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.60,0:18:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sip.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permintaan selesai dengan sukses.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.44,0:18:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari sudah hampir malam,\Nmari kita berkemah di tempat kemarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.15,0:18:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.60,0:18:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Malam ini pun, berdua lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.15,0:18:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berarti aku benar-benar tak boleh\Nmelepas topeng ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.26,0:18:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Misi telah tuntas.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:18:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan Pendekar Pedang Sihir Kilat Hitam
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.10,0:19:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan Cecily si Pemandu Kasih Sayang ini,\Nsemuanya beres.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.33,0:19:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Adaw!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak butuh julukan seperti itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal itu keren...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.88,0:19:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, mana laporannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.64,0:19:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini laporan tertulisnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.73,0:19:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Isinya luar biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Laporan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.26,0:19:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah cukup secara lisan saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.84,0:19:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena banyak orang malas sepertimu,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}permintaan semacam ini tak bisa\Ndiserahkan pada sembarang orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.73,0:19:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memang pantas untuk Nona... eh, bukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.68,0:19:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudku, Cecily.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begini, laporannya bisa\Nlangsung kuserahkan, sangat membantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini imbalannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.80,0:19:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beginilah Misi Peringkat A,\Njumlahnya lumayan banyak, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.08,0:19:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kalau kita rayakan\Nkeberhasilan ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.31,0:19:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ide bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.66,0:19:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi sebelum itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sebaiknya Tuan Pendekar Pedang Sihir\Nganti baju dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.40,0:19:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm? Pintunya tidak dikunci?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:20:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dewa Pelindung ada di mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.51,0:20:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selama empat hari ini,\Naku selalu datang tiap hari,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.02,0:20:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi beliau tidak ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.37,0:20:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kumohon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.24,0:20:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kau tahu, tolong beri tahu aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.84,0:20:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di mana Dewa Pelindung berada?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.95,0:20:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bocah, kau sudah kembali?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.93,0:20:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Goy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suara itu... Dewa Pelindung?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, ini aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.29,0:20:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dewa Pelindung!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.04,0:20:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tidak ada di sini, aku sangat khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.77,0:20:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf aku tidak memberitahumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.93,0:20:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya aku menyewa kamar di dekat sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah menjadi petualang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.55,0:20:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang aku bisa mencari uang sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.81,0:20:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi ke depannya, kau tak perlu\Nmemaksakan diri belikan aku Batu Sihir lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.93,0:20:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak memaksakan diri!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.44,0:21:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Melayani Dewa Pelindung adalah\Nkebahagiaan terbesar bagiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.20,0:21:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi kumohon, biarkan aku terus merawatmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.44,0:21:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.32,0:21:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.08,0:21:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku juga akan membalas budi padamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.17,0:21:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mana mungkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.28,0:21:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Asalkan bisa bersamamu...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anu, kami juga ada di sini, lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.68,0:21:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Teal sampai akhir tak memedulikan\NPendekar Pedang Sihir atau Cecily.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.06,0:21:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia cuma melihat Goy saja, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.71,0:21:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, rasanya aku lelah sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.60,0:21:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Youki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ti-Tidak bisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.82,0:21:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasa malu selama empat hari ini\Ndampaknya terlalu besar!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.86,0:21:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Identitas ini resmi disegel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.74,0:21:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu sebentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.86,0:21:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.28,0:21:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memang benar Tuan Pendekar Pedang Sihir itu\Nsuka bertindak gegabah,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.26,0:21:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}terlalu mencolok,\Ndan sering merepotkan, tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.17,0:22:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berkat sihirmu,\Nmisi kali ini berjalan dengan aman.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.11,0:22:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebagai Cecily sang petualang,\Naku ingin bekerja sama denganmu lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cecily sang petualang.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.01,0:22:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sihirku tak hanya sebatas itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.77,0:22:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kau tertarik,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.31,0:22:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}akan kutunjukkan kekuatanku\Nyang lebih hebat lagi di misi berikutnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.31,0:22:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan menantikannya.
